room_title: Escape room "Lost in Space" by Exit Strategy in Charlotte
room_address: 4215 Stuart Andrew Blvd Ste B, Charlotte NC 28217
room_description: After a space mission gone wrong, the team is tasked with working together to repair the ship and seek rescue through the escape hatch before they run out of oxygen and their time expires. Stranded in space, will you survive before the air runs out?
